<p style="padding:5px 0;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;margin:0;">What does it mean to be a trillionaire in dollars? Until recently, it was inconceivable for most people, but not all. The <a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/mattdurot/2026/06/12/spacexs-ipo-just-made-elon-musk-the-worlds-first-trillionaire/"style="text-decoration: underline; color: #b61313 !important;">SpaceX IPO</a> made a lot of people very financially happy, but it made one man&mdash;Elon Musk&mdash;wealthy beyond what a good chunk of the earth&rsquo;s inhabitants can conceive. One question I have: what&rsquo;s he going to do with all that money? What can anyone do with all that money?</p>
<p style="padding:5px 0;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;margin:0;">It&rsquo;s a good reminder to lock in this week: you won&rsquo;t become a trillionaire, but maybe you can hustle towards millionaire status.</p>
